 ### Test 1: fără slug → auto-derivare ("Primăria Focșani" → "primaria-focsani"). Așteptat 200
POST {{host}}/api/Provisioning
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginSuperAdmin.response.body.$.token}}

{
  "denumire": "Primăria Focșani",
  "judet": "Vrancea",
  "codSiruta": "176410",
  "tip": 2,
  "slug": null,
  "emailAdmin": "admin.focsani@cleriq.ro",
  "parolaAdmin": "AdminFocsani1!",
  "numeCompletAdmin": "Admin Focșani"
}

### Test 2: slug explicit care produce conflict cu Slobozia. Așteptat 409 cu sugestii
POST {{host}}/api/Provisioning
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginSuperAdmin.response.body.$.token}}

{
  "denumire": "Test Conflict",
  "judet": "Ialomița",
  "codSiruta": "999999",
  "tip": 1,
  "slug": "primaria-slobozia",
  "emailAdmin": "test@cleriq.ro",
  "parolaAdmin": "Test12345!",
  "numeCompletAdmin": "Test"
}

### Test 3: slug invalid (majuscule + spațiu). Așteptat 400 cu mesaj despre format
POST {{host}}/api/Provisioning
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginSuperAdmin.response.body.$.token}}

{
  "denumire": "Test Format",
  "judet": "Ialomița",
  "codSiruta": "888888",
  "tip": 1,
  "slug": "Test Slug",
  "emailAdmin": "test2@cleriq.ro",
  "parolaAdmin": "Test12345!",
  "numeCompletAdmin": "Test"
}

### Test 4: slug rezervat ("admin"). Așteptat 400 cu mesaj „rezervat"
POST {{host}}/api/Provisioning
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginSuperAdmin.response.body.$.token}}

{
  "denumire": "Test Rezervat",
  "judet": "Ialomița",
  "codSiruta": "777777",
  "tip": 1,
  "slug": "admin",
  "emailAdmin": "test3@cleriq.ro",
  "parolaAdmin": "Test12345!",
  "numeCompletAdmin": "Test"
}



